        <li>Ensure the content adheres to the guidelines specified in Section 2.</li>
        <li>Not misuse the platform for purposes other than simplifying terms and conditions documents.</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>Uploading unauthorized content may result in account suspension or termination.</p>
      
      <h3>4. No Legal Advice</h3>
      <p>The summaries generated by the app are provided for informational purposes only and do not constitute legal advice. You should always consult a qualified attorney for specific legal guidance.</p>
      
      <h3>5. Prohibited Uses</h3>
      <p>You may not use the app for:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Processing any content other than Terms and Conditions documents.</li>
        <li>Uploading fraudulent, deceptive, or harmful material.</li>
        <li>Engaging in illegal or unauthorized activities.</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>Violation of these rules may result in immediate suspension or termination of your account.</p>
      
